! Release History

!! Version 1.0.0 (November 2025)

Initial public release with full feature set:

!!! Core Features
* 501, 301, 180, and Cricket game types
* Multi-player support with dynamic add/remove
* Real-time scoring with automatic calculations
* Bust detection and win detection
* Game history with timestamps
* Player statistics tracking

!!! User Interface
* TiddlyWiki-inspired styling
* DXC Purple theme branding
* Responsive design for all devices
* Touch-friendly mobile interface
* Keyboard shortcut support

!!! Technical Improvements
* WCAG Level A compliance (accessibility)
* Valid HTML5 structure
* Cross-browser compatibility
* Self-contained single-file application
* No external dependencies

!!! Infrastructure
* GitHub Actions for automated testing
* Cross-platform validation (Windows, Linux)
* HTML validation pipeline
* Automated release generation
* GitHub Pages deployment

!! Planned Features

Future versions may include:

* Additional game types (Around the Clock, etc.)
* Tournament bracket management
* Export/import game history
* Custom themes
* Sound effects (optional)
* Print-friendly scoresheets

